it says the input should be [6,1,5,5]

But it doesn't say that. It reads:

Expected 4-dimensional input for 4-dimensional weight [6, 1, 5, 5], 
but got input of size [64, 32, 32] instead

It says that the input dimension should match the weight dimension.

body:
> it says the input should be [6,1,5,5]

But it doesn't say that. It reads:
```
Expected 4-dimensional input for 4-dimensional weight [6, 1, 5, 5], 
but got input of size [64, 32, 32] instead
```

It says that the input dimension should match the weight dimension.
